So, now we have come to the topic of the main information problems

01:04:07.000 --> 01:04:11.000
that are facing the heads of Russian enterprises today.

01:04:12.000 --> 01:04:19.000
Of course, now there is such a stage in the development of our Russian business,

01:04:19.000 --> 01:04:25.000
